  <description type="morphology">Plants 3–15(–25) dm. Aerial flowering stems 2–4 dm, tomentose to glabrate. Leaves: petiole (1–)2–4 cm; blade lanceolate to narrowly oblong, 5–8 × 1–2 cm. Inflorescences open, 10–50 cm wide. Involucres 4–5 mm. Flowers 3–4 mm. Achenes 3–3.5 mm.</description>
